<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Login - Nexus Inc.</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/img/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
</head>
<body>
    
    <%- include('partials/nav') %>

    <main>
        <section id="login" class="contato-section" style="min-height: calc(100vh - 80px); justify-content: center;">
            <div class="container-lettering">
                <h2>Acesse sua <span class="destaque-contato">Conta</span></h2>
                <p>Bem-vindo de volta! Insira suas credenciais para acessar o portal.</p>
                
                <form class="contato-box" action="/login" method="post">
                    
                    <div class="texto-box">
                        <label for="email">E-mail corporativo</label>
                        <input type="email" autocomplete="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="contato@empresa.com" required>
                    </div>

                    <div class="texto-box">
                        <label for="senha">Senha</label>
                        <input type="password" autocomplete="current-password" id="senha" name="senha" placeholder="Senha" required>
                    </div>
                    
                    <button type="submit" class="botao-solicitar">Entrar no Portal</button>
                    
                    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 25px;">
                        <p style="color: #CBD5E1; font-size: 0.95rem;">
                            Ainda não tem uma conta? <a href="/cadastro" style="color: #7DD3FC; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Cadastre-se aqui</a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

</body>
</html>